OL,3,CWhale song has its own 'phonetic
OL,4,Calphabet', research shows
OL,6,FThe whales also vary the rhythm and
OL,7,Ftempo of their clicks, adding an extra
OL,8,Flayer of complexity and meaning.
OL,10,F"This marks a profound moment in
OL,11,Fadvancing our understanding of sperm
OL,12,Fwhales," Dr David Gruber, the founder
OL,13,Fof the long-term study, called Project
OL,14,FCETI, said. "It opens up the
OL,15,Fpossibility that sperm whales have an
OL,16,Fincredibly complex and nuanced
OL,17,Fcommunication system."
