OL,3,CWhale song has its own 'phonetic
OL,4,Calphabet', research shows
OL,6,FTo get enough examples of the sperm
OL,7,Fwhale clicks in Dominica, where there
OL,8,Fis a population of around 200 whales,
OL,9,Fscientists created a giant underwater
OL,10,Fstudio with microphones at different
OL,11,Fdepths.
OL,13,FTags on the whales also record what
OL,14,Fposition they are in while clicking -
OL,15,Ffor example diving, sleeping, or
OL,16,Fbreathing at the surface - and whether
OL,17,Fother whales are nearby.
