OL,6,FScientists hope they will one day be
OL,7,Fable to understand what sperm whales
OL,8,Fare trying to communicate. That
OL,9,Fknowledge could be used for
OL,10,Fconservation purposes, like minimising
OL,11,Ftheir risk of being hit by ships or
OL,12,Freducing ocean noise levels.
